item.title: SE4: EP 23 Fracture Proof Your Bones
item.description:
Osteoporosis is common.

80% of osteoporosis cases are in women, and the majority of those are in post-menopausal women when the rate of bone loss is at its fastest.

Research indicates that approximately 1 in 10 women over the age of 60 are affected worldwide and this is likely to increase as our global population ages.
